OL,5, People who witness traumatic incidents 
OL,6, including terror attacks will be       
OL,7, offered similar support to bereaved    
OL,8, families, the government has confirmed.
OL,10,FThose hit by crimes like the Manchester
OL,11,FArena bomb would be helped, as would   
OL,12,Fchildren in the wider community, the   
OL,13,FMinistry of Justice (MOJ) said.        
OL,15,FThe government-funded National Homicide
OL,16,FService commissions counselling, legal 
OL,17,Fhelp and restorative justice.          
OL,19,FOpposition parties have called for     
OL,20,Fvictims to be given far more support.  
